{
  "texts": [
    "This technique has also been broadened to support continual learning environments, as illustrated in recent research 25, 26.",
    "Current research focuses on dynamic prompt tuning, which adapts prompts in real time based on evolving contexts, as well as hierarchical prompt tuning, which provides multilevel control over the model's responses 27, 28.",
    "Prefix tuning is another powerful technique that adds learnable parameters as prefixes to the input of pretrained models, enabling modification to different applications with minimal changes to the model itself 21.",
    "This method enables efficient domain-specific fine-tuning without requiring the retraining of the entire model, particularly in resource-limited settings.",
    "Recent innovations introduce hierarchical prefix tuning, which organizes prefixes in a hierarchical manner to provide more detailed control over the model's responses 29."
  ]
}